PROP_PASSIVE_USER_ID

static final String PROP_PASSIVE_USER_ID
Property for setting the username used for the anonymous user. The anonymous user is used when IsPassive is true, and the user is not signed in at the IdP.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

PROP_FORCE_AUTHN_URLS

static final String PROP_FORCE_AUTHN_URLS
A comma separated list of urls for which ForceAuthn should be set to true. Each url is treated as a regular expression against the request (without the servlet path).
